divs: sighting detailsi was at home, outside because i couldn't sleep, something had woken both myself and my partner up. my partner was with me, but he didn't see the light.i was already looking up at the night sky because it was slightly cloudy and had been raining earlier in the day. it just flashed once, as if someone had turned on a flood light. very bright almost double of the brightest star\planet. at first i was in disbelief but quickly started becoming very curious as to what the source of light was.

Summary: Just seen a very bright flash, brighter than any star. Then it disappeared as quickly as it came.
